OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry and settled with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine, warm by afternoon. Patchy
OL,8,Fovernight low cloud in the north and
OL,9,Feast.
